{"tid":752070,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"菅野美穗高齡懷二胎！堺雅人「奶粉錢加倍」網民呼籲趕拍半澤續集","createTime":"2018-07-22T13:11:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T05:55:12.000Z","uid":9573,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6c20221c40a54a898019bd10677f7d76b9afef3f","tid":752070,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T13:11:58.000Z","msg":"40歲日本女星菅野美穗懷第二胎！她2013年4月嫁給堺雅人，2015年生下第一個兒子，19日透過經紀公司官網宣布懷孕，外傳已經懷孕5個月，胎兒進入安定期才發表消息，年底就會迎接第二個寶寶出生啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3427/d3427622.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3427%2Fd3427622.jpg&h=23d24619&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲菅野美穗懷第二胎，老公堺雅人開心到爆。<br />\n<br />\n據日媒《報知體育》報導，菅野美穗低調向朋友、相關人士透露懷二胎的消息，19日中午透過官網正式宣布懷孕，特別提到「在這個年紀懷孕、生產，一定有很多人擔心，但是又增加一個家人的喜悅，還要再等一段漫長的時間，我的丈夫、兒子，對這腹中的新生命注入很多力量。」她37歲懷第一胎，當時傳出歸功於婦產科女醫宋美玄賜招「常做就會有」，這次40歲再度懷孕，己隊已經擁有了新球季所需的一切，領隊高普宣布已經組軍完畢。日前剛被拍到和老公、大兒子一起外出散步，原來當時就已經懷孕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3427/d3427626.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3427%2Fd3427626.jpg&h=a79848e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼菅野美穗宣布懷二胎喜訊。<br />\n<br />\n堺雅人婚後憑《半澤直樹》爆紅，創下日劇史上的新高紀錄，愛妻菅野美穗被業界大讚幫夫運強。他從配角榮登一線男主角後，戲約、廣告約都應接不暇，私下仍非常照顧老婆、兒子，幫忙分擔家事，現在要迎接第二個孩子出生，養兒奶粉錢更是倍增，網友留言祝賀也趁機敲碗「恭喜！《半澤直樹》也拜託了」、「一定要順產」、「期待生個健康寶寶！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3427/d3427624.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3427%2Fd3427624.jpg&h=e5bd4f9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲菅野美穗懷第二胎，網友敲碗堺雅人接《半澤直樹》續集。"},{"pid":"56f2159b5b4d04388964c499c5730adf2d0d1e53","tid":752070,"uid":87573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T13:14:14.000Z","msg":"高普<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b3f75982e09a8e142d80f25d874af087a2f10cf","tid":752070,"uid":45213,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T02:52:19.000Z","msg":"不如拍legal high3<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd1cbce6d928f33cc2f3bd885b463a25c9e2232","tid":752070,"uid":5475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8b3f75982e09a8e142d80f25d874af087a2f10cf","tid":752070,"uid":45213,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T02:52:19.000Z","msg":"不如拍legal high3<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T02:57:08.000Z","msg":"legal high x 信用欺詐師<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d52e939e72278e20e90f0bd9017a4e8b29e1bf42","tid":752070,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:41:42.000Z","msg":"認真，如果冇吸引既故事，就唔好拍續集啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n費事拍爛"},{"pid":"125a75613b40cdd807db6438b52e4f7d32b5e3f6","tid":752070,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:44:37.000Z","msg":"同結衣合作"},{"pid":"fc7fa91c7b0739ab2764a58bd129391367e8a29c","tid":752070,"uid":193555,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:47:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"227b6f6198d9b910f697c68b1f34f70f5bc792d0","tid":752070,"uid":154725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:55:12.000Z","msg":"己隊已經擁有了新球季所需的一切，領隊高普宣布已經組軍完畢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}